title: Tom Cloarec's Road to Victory, ASP European pro junior in Royan.
description: " Beginning of July the ASP European pro junior season 2013 has started with an amazing win of Tom Cloarec at the Royan Atlantique pro Junior. What a great start for Tom who claimed his first ASP event of his young carreer. Here is a little clip tracing his run threw that contest... Obviously MR Cloarec seems to have fun and looks strong as we are jumping in the second event of the season the O'Neill Sopelana pro Junior... Watch him carefully, 2013 could be his year..."
